8
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:30,320
In my fourth year of university, I actually got a panic attack.

9
00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:37,280
>> In this episode, we dive into how Anya turned a very painful experience into an app that has generated over a million dollars.

10
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:43,120
